OL,3,CHow buy now pay later schemes are
OL,4,Cpushing families into debt
OL,6,FAround half of shoppers say they'll
OL,7,Fuse these schemes to pay for their
OL,8,FChristmas goods, without always
OL,9,Frealising it's a form of short-term
OL,10,Fborrowing which could damage their
OL,11,Fcredit rating, as ITV News'
OL,12,FCharanpreet Khaira reports
OL,14,FBuy Now Pay Later has become a
OL,15,Ffamiliar option at the checkout. It
OL,16,Fallows shoppers to split the cost of a
OL,17,Fpurchase over weeks or months, often
OL,18,Finterest-free.
