OL,3,CHow buy now pay later schemes are
OL,4,Cpushing families into debt
OL,6,FFor many rushing to finish their
OL,7,FChristmas shopping, it can feel like a
OL,8,Fharmless way to spread the cost.
OL,10,FBut new figures shared exclusively
OL,11,Fwith ITV News suggest the bill is
OL,12,Fcatching up with a growing number of
OL,13,Fhouseholds.
OL,15,FMore than #33 million of Buy Now Pay
OL,16,FLater (BNPL) debt was written off in
OL,17,Fthe past year ` a 73% increase on the
OL,18,Fyear before.
