OL,3,CHow buy now pay later schemes are
OL,4,Cpushing families into debt
OL,6,FBNPL allows shoppers to delay or
OL,7,Fspread payments, often interest-free.
OL,8,FWhat's less obvious is that it's a
OL,9,Fform of short-term credit - and one
OL,10,Fthat is now easier than ever to use.
OL,12,FJaquilina, a single mother of two,
OL,13,Fsays BNPL once felt like a sensible
OL,14,Fsolution - especially at Christmas,
OL,15,Fwhen, like many of us, she felt
OL,16,Fpressure to spend more than she could
OL,17,Fafford.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
