OL,3,CHow buy now pay later schemes are
OL,4,Cpushing families into debt
OL,6,F"I started buying things like shoes
OL,7,Fand clothes for my kids," she told ITV
OL,8,FNews. "You think, I'll pay in 30 days
OL,9,F- I'll deal with it later."
OL,11,FOver several years, she estimates she
OL,12,Fspent around #4,000 using BNPL
OL,13,Fschemes. Missed payments soon led to
OL,14,Flate fees, reminders, and growing
OL,15,Fanxiety.
OL,17,F"You receive those letters, those
OL,18,Femails, those reminders, and you need
OL,19,Fto feed the kids, keep up with the
OL,20,Fbills.
