OL,3,CHow buy now pay later schemes are
OL,4,Cpushing families into debt
OL,6,FOnce largely limited to online
OL,7,Fshopping, BNPL is now appearing on the
OL,8,Fhigh street too, with lenders offering
OL,9,Fphysical cards that allow shoppers to
OL,10,Fspread the cost at the till.
OL,12,FCharities warn this makes borrowing
OL,13,Feasier - without people fully
OL,14,Fregistering what they are taking on -
OL,15,Fparticularly at Christmas, when the
OL,16,FMoney Advice Trust says one in four
OL,17,Fadults feels pressured to overspend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
