OL,3,CHow buy now pay later schemes are
OL,4,Cpushing families into debt
OL,6,FBoth Money Wellness and the Money
OL,7,FAdvice Trust expect demand for their
OL,8,Fcall centres to spike in the New Year,
OL,9,Fwhen festive spending catches up and
OL,10,Frepayments fall due.
OL,12,FFrom July 2026, the government plans
OL,13,Fto introduce new rules requiring BNPL
OL,14,Fproviders to carry out affordability
OL,15,Fchecks and giving consumers the right
OL,16,Fto complain to the Financial Ombudsman
OL,17,Fif they face problems.
