OL,3,CHow buy now pay later schemes are
OL,4,Cpushing families into debt
OL,6,FMick McAteer, from the Financial
OL,7,FInclusion Centre, told ITV News the
OL,8,Fregulation "won't address the issue of
OL,9,Fmaking it too easy to borrow and too
OL,10,Feasy to spend."
OL,12,FHe added that it would not stop BNPL
OL,13,Fcompanies from targeting consumers
OL,14,Fthrough retailers and social media.
OL,16,FA Treasury spokesperson said adverts
OL,17,Fmust already be clear that BNPL is a
OL,18,Fform of credit.
OL,20,FITV News contacted the UK's largest
OL,21,FBuy Now Pay Later providers.
