OL,3,CHow buy now pay later schemes are
OL,4,Cpushing families into debt
OL,6,FThose who responded said most
OL,7,Fcustomers use their products
OL,8,Fresponsibly and repay on time, with
OL,9,Fchecks in place to ensure payments are
OL,10,Fmanageable.
OL,12,FBut charities warn it is the most
OL,13,Fvulnerable who can fall between the
OL,14,Fcracks - and for whom the impact of
OL,15,Fmounting debt can be most severe.
